{"tid":1451870,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇方法救前線 （打機攻略？）","createTime":"2019-08-11T21:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:23:24.000Z","uid":167082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1f177c7b0cfd6eb54e6812bac2419b953837d4dd","tid":1451870,"uid":167082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:26:46.000Z","msg":"小弟自認係冇膽匪類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打機企黎企去都係第5-6排唔敢上最前，以下係我見到嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n打機嗰時，速龍一衝，唔係前排跑得慢，係中後排慢（其實都唔係，係好7多人，d人唔知要退）前排塞住曬，速龍就隨便扯一個背囊，猛打再拘捕，屌你見d速龍一個一個咁搣d前線出黎暴打再拘捕真係唔知點做。但係冇中後排實死，因為前排一定比人包。有冇策略拖延俾d時間人退。<br />\n    1. 灑菜油？鋼珠？（唔知有冇用）<br />\n    2. 汽油彈掉地下？（其實最有用，但一定比人話暴徒暴徒，有機失民心）<br />\n    3. 反速龍部隊，幾十個敢死隊衝出去打7佢地（要夠多人，d人要夠泡，dllm往死裏打）<br />\n真係冇d好d嘅辦法？小弟愚笨，希望有人教教我打機應該點打怪獸。"},{"pid":"9d7976ab092192735c23af1ef0157dd5570e4624","tid":1451870,"uid":167082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:30:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae57288bffe27806914de46cfcf6f8f070c4a53","tid":1451870,"uid":167082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:31:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa6617904e34e0a43531c1178182b6f9f2618dbe","tid":1451870,"uid":167082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:31:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9418af0ed2477382cb33eb6f18bc7ae3a51950a","tid":1451870,"uid":167082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:31:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1494726325c16722e56135529eed5d09781f4f3","tid":1451870,"uid":167082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T21:32:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmo